Class GenerateElements<OBJ>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gaffer.operation.AbstractOperation<CloseableIterable<OBJ>,CloseableIterable<Element>>
      • gaffer.operation.impl.generate.GenerateElements<OBJ>
  • Type Parameters:
    OBJ - the type of objects in the input iterable.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Operation<CloseableIterable<OBJ>,CloseableIterable<Element>>

    public class GenerateElements<OBJ>
extends AbstractOperation<CloseableIterable<OBJ>,CloseableIterable<Element>>
    An GenerateElements operation generates an CloseableIterable of Elements from an CloseableIterable of objects.
